    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "chitmas",
      "1964\nWhile dining aloft,\nTo you we say,\n\"The Merriest, Cheeriest\nChristmas Day.\"\nUNITED AIR LINES\nMenu\nThis menu prepared in United Air Lines Flight Kitchen\nat Chicago—O'Hare International Airport,\nEdwin Wirz, Chef.\nShrimp Cocktail\nGreen Pea Soup\nWafers\nRoast Breast of Turkey,\nCelery and Mushroom Dressing,\nGiblet Gravy\nGlazed Sweet Potatoes\nButtered French Cut Green Beans\nClub Roll, Buttercrust Roll\nor Salt Stick\nKentucky Salad\nRose Wine Dressing\nAssorted French Pastry\nor Petits Fours\nCoffee\nTea\nMilk\nSanka\nDinner Mint"
    ],
